Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The star of a show is usually charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the same could be said for the culprit or victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An statue of an angel without a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys go to a mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and find themselves in a bizarre labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we felt the same light the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, lots and lots of the same emotions filled our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the signals you sent destroyed my theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These feelings were always beyond your reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's fight, go against our morals...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And aim for a wider world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if this town changes someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what would an elementary schooler be sighing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan! Come here, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone asked us Detective Boys for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this time it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute? Even her clothes are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Angel's Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a man who calls himself "Tokei."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tokei," as in clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no first or last name, just "Tokei."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man is your mother's grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he is your great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Isegawa Gozoushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great-grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's actually someone else in my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With resilience, he dominated Japan's\Nstock market after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:05.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Corrida means "bullfight" in Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's been referred to as "corrida."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a legendary speculator who\Nearned a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tokei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who solves this riddle will inherit\Nall properties of the corrida."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the time limit is 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the time limit is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the person will lose the right to both inherit and accede.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entrants include my wife, my\Nsons, and my grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The order is determined by their order of heirship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to supervise this and make\Nsure my wishes are carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything else to say, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, no one comes to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time left, and yet\NI have to endure such loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself. Your body can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm already like this, yet they still won't come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were my great-grandfather's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Isegawa Gozoushi's secretary and\Nthe deliverer of the testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsunaka Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your turn as the seventeenth heiress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you can choose whether or not to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:05:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, isn't there a group called\Nthe "Detective Boys" at your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told you to come to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we accept the\Ncommission to solve the riddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we would also be accepting the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did your family say, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad got in a car accident not long after I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and last year my mother became very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I am all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the opposition between the families,\Nmy father and mother went far away and eloped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I don't know any other relatives, I came to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how do you feel about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I accept this challenge to solve the riddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get to see where my great-grandfather\Nand my morn lived when she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The house is called Angel's Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and all of you Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really far away, this Angel's Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be there shortly once we get out of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already told your parents that you're\Ngoing camping for a couple days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he has already done some research on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see it. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Angel of the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Angel of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Angel of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, that's the Angel of the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is said that every one of them is facing\Neither north, south, east, or west.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every angel also has the face of\NMadam when she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great-grandmother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Without even a second thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam left for another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The children were left with the cold-hearted father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After they grew up, they all left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eventually, he was the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even when some of his children\Ncame to visit him on occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they quarreled restlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a sad man that no one understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:46.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE7E7EB&\fade(0,400)}Southern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The southern mansion is guarded by the southern angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's also the house where my lord passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the west mansion is typically where we work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:54.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE7E7EB&}Western Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:57.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE7E7EB&\fade(400,400)}Northern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The north mansion is where the children and servants live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all In really good condition even\Nthough no one's living there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've always been keeping them up and caring for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The east mansion looks like ghosts\Ncould be haunting the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE7E7EB&\fade(0,400)}Eastern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My lord decreed no one's allowed\Nto approach that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Minotauros.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minotauros?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The legendary monster whose body\Nwas half man and half bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was the speculator called "corrida"\Nwho dominated the stock market,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's a very suitable decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Everywhere I look... Bulls, bulls, and more bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the stock market world, the bull\Nrepresents strength and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even in the center of finance, New York's Wall\NStreet, a copper statue of an bull is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to your great-grandfather, the bull was a protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's one of the security devices my lord left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It starts up automatically when the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has it been like this since Isegawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, as long as the treasure and the riddle are still here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the security devices and I will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The angel's really scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the day, it's the angel's mansion. At\Nnight, it becomes the witch's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.30,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBEC1C0&\fade(0,400)}Mansion of Corrida
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid, I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too. I will do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Fifth House that sits in the\Nmiddle of the angel's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is usually referred to as the Mansion of Corrida."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? My mother used to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After your parents left the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My lord was always worried about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would always wonder whether\Nor not they would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us the riddle that Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s\Ngreat-grandfather left with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's not time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the riddle has something\Nto do with the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, have dinner and rest in the north mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.43,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBEC1C0&\fade(0,400)}Northern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...for me to announce the riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"and its tail becomes its head,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"the angel comes down and starts playing the horn."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That melody is my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And its tail becomes its head,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"the angel comes down and starts playing the horn."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what was that last part...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That melody is my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 24 hour time limit begins now and\Nends at nine tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, which bull is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traps that are even more horrific\Nthan the security devices my lord installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some participants got lost and injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My lord's mansion is also called a huge labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be that really big bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not a good idea to act by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time we just go along with Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you feel ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That phrase when the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must mean that bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must mean the horn opens a hole in its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that horn must have a map inside\Nthat says where the treasure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.07,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBEC1C0&}Mansion of Corrida
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous to act by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} smile at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to help her solve her great-grandfather's riddle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, how could you help\Nher without looking at this bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And its tail becomes its head,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bull's horn disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The angel that comes down must be the Angel of the West!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said the Angel of the West is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to be a "director to our original goal."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean we need to keep trying to reach\Nour original goal until the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:57.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: "Director" and "carry through" sound similar in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be "carry through to our original goal", Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think something's suspicious\Nabout the eastern mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My lord decreed that no one is allowed\Nto approach that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this whole riddle was made up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the treasure is actually in the eastern mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gen-Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE3E5E5&}Eastern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE3E5E5&\fade(0,400)}Angel of the West
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could the angel come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...looking for right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A power grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, someone's trying to make us go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's in the eastern mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The treasure must be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bull has no horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And its tail becomes its head,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its tail becomes its head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open, open...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-help me! I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this fireplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deep inside, there's a sk-skeleton!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be an unknown thief that\Ngot lost and died in the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-but if we don't call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand, I will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, don't waste your valuable time anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.45,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE3E5E5&}Northern Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all asked to go to the bathroom a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is no one back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll walk around a bit, then come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, no one comes to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time left, and yet\NI have to endure such loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can't hold it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where is the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we trust what Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this stuff about the great-grandfather, the riddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is the seventeenth heiress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in the recent past months,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There have been already 16 challengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no note, no record...or any clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't the story have just been made up\Nto trick Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} into coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick her into coming here, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think Tokei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just have this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One thing's for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the previous challengers did leave some clues,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man has erased them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's so all the challengers are on equal terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what's his reason for doing so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, only ten hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For causing you all trouble, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there are many other bulls to check in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we still have ten hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely find that bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll break its horn to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it a bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's that line... "the bull's horn disappears..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s great-grandfather\Nwas referred to as "corrida."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night in that Mansion of Corrida,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was within an inch of falling off that bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was an bull with horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there a decorative golden bull\Nwith horns in the East Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you were extremely scared of that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! Why would I be "extremely scared" of such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so mean to say, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bull in that riddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...isn't a particular bull in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The horn of the bull disappears," that is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sh-Sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the character "go", which means noon."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, if it refers to the Chinese\Nzodiac, it would mean horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any horses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not related to animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This "go" indicates a direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the other thing is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HE7E9E4&}Angel of the South
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Angel of the South...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this case, "go" means south.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a power grid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deductions are right, it's not dangerous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because "go" also means 12:00pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the noon in "noonday."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's stuck, so I can't pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the treasure the riddle was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This crystal is the key to solving the next part of the riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the bull's horn disappears,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And its tail becomes its head..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would point to the character "ne."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The direction of "ne" is north.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the next clue must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the Angel of the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hurry and-!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In all those days where a future was unsure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I fell in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to stay loving you forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by stopping the time echoing in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be scared of being together with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I can't change others or the past
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can change myself and my dreams for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorrow piles up in the darkening city
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forever in a warm and soft breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll be together, believing in each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,June Bride, I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That skeleton you found in the Eastern Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way was its head facing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the skeleton was the infamous burglar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is the time limit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we still need to solve the next part of the riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: The Mysterious Angel's Mansion, Part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:22.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll solve the puzzle so Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nand I can bull it up together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.80,0:24:23.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:24.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:25.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm fired up!
